> rust, and prep the metal in a preferable manner.  I'm also seeing a lot of
> wincing at rattle can primers.  I'm totally open to suggestion I just don't
> want to be pissed when I pay someone to lay the paint on it and, well you
> know.  I also don't see being able to media blast the whole thing down to
> the sparkling skin and just prime right over it with the patching and work
